query:
SELECT id
        FROM workout_data 
        WHERE user_id = $1
        AND workout_start IS NOT NULL
        AND workout_end IS NOT NULL
        AND ABS(EXTRACT(EPOCH FROM (workout_start - $2))::float8) <= $4
        AND ABS(EXTRACT(EPOCH FROM (workout_end - $3))::float8) <= $4
        LIMIT 1
